--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[Square Font]
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	every time the screen is refreshed, we expand the image to make each 
	character squarish

	instead we can remove this code and just implement a new .ttf file (true type 
	font) that is already expanded

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[Font Rendering]
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	Use opengl with character maps
	This should greatly increase the speed of rendering

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[Send Blueprints]
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	When a user creates a new ship/item its blueprint will be sent to the
	server which will then distribute that blueprint to which ever clients need
	to render it on their screen

	This will let the server merely send updates to the blueprint when it is
	modified by the client, the server can then distribute a diff of the old
	and new blueprints to all other clients that need it

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[Client Map Download]
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	The server will generate a map procedurally and make sure it all works.
	The client can then send all the seed values for the procedural content to
	client who can then reproduce the map exactly

	Planet textures can be generated procedurally using but a few seed values
